{"tid":1969533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣日月潭推蒸口罩服務捱轟　不足3天撤回","createTime":"2020-04-12T13:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T15:06:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c08bcf2e905d593dc34a6ddc37d86117f3faa0b","tid":1969533,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200412/s00004/4fa012f0dcfaf55b3ea428ca53073e87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200412%2Fs00004%2F4fa012f0dcfaf55b3ea428ca53073e87.jpg&h=0dbe7779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n口罩不應重用，「蒸口罩論」更備受質疑。在台灣，日月潭伊達邵遊客中心前日（10日）推出免費代蒸口罩服務，隨即被轟恐造成防疫破口，中心今日（12日）宣布取消蒸口罩服務。<br />\n<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，日月潭伊達邵遊客中心與外判廠商合作，推出代蒸口罩服務，被當地傳媒質疑「多人共用電鍋有交叉感染風險」、「民眾自行使用恐成防疫破口」。<br />\n<br />\n日月潭國家風景區管理處伊達邵管理站主任陳逸全今早先澄清，蒸口罩服務由專人操作，非民眾自行使用；他下午再表示，已撤回蒸口罩服務，並承認推出前未有徵詢衛生部門或醫生意見。"},{"pid":"e3af42af2e7363818162d6d3701310b00bd9dd6e","tid":1969533,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200412/s00004/1586693294871/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00004%2F1586693294871%2F&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=881958e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00004%2F1586693294871%2F&h=91f08029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200412/s00004/1586693294871/</a>"},{"pid":"8b915050fc8252e505792c214966a212dbc7b7d2","tid":1969533,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:13:28.000Z","msg":"台灣口罩供應都唔緊張,<br />\n蒸黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3756fec79855dbf9aa2927306b72b70496212a36","tid":1969533,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"店長被蔣元秋誤導，我深表同情"},{"pid":"51db4e28887543e2fff8cc081133868000a217c5","tid":1969533,"uid":26424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rtSVMff/IMG-20200412-230041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FrtSVMff%2FIMG-20200412-230041.jpg&h=ebb80da7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d74b9131ca12980678415dfd1f1134a4734714c","tid":1969533,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"係唔係睇完香港ANN姐蒸口罩想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}